              <td> 
                <p class="blacklink" style="text-align: justify;">Glodyne has its unique redefined employee  band structure in the organization. It creates a view towards lean and flat  organization. The employee band is designed for internal brand building in  three bands across organization. The employee band layers are termed as</p>
                <ol>
                  <li class="blacklink">Strategy Band</li>
                  <li class="blacklink">Professional Band </li>
                  <li class="blacklink">Execution Band</li>
                </ol>
                <p class="blacklink" style="text-align: justify;">Objective: Employee band is created to  identify core competencies of employees and classify them accordingly. The  employee band is to seen as circular (hand in hand) highlighting inter  dependence of the bands. All the bands enjoy equal sense of importance and  status. </p></td>
            </tr>
